      • SystemCheckExam

        private java.lang.Object[] SystemCheckExam()
        Called from BuildSolvedExamObject method and runs all over student's answers for each question in the exam and return an Object[]. Object[0]=HashMap(QuestionInExam,Integer) which contains the question in exam as key and the student's answer index as value. Object[1]=Student's grade for exam.
        Returns:
        Object[] studentAnsersAndScoreForExam
